        <abstract>
            <p>The outbreak of war and war work have interfered with JVC’s scientific work.</p> 
<p>Publisher does not, however, think the war will hurt success of <hi rend="italic">Descent</hi> in Germany, and JVC asks for corrected sheets for his use in translating it.</p> 
            <p>Wishes struggle between Romanic and Teutonic races could be fought out in a form more appropriate to their cultures and civilisation.</p>
        </abstract>
